Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,You've finally settled down.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.85,0:00:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sheesh, what a handful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.39,0:00:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but having to bring him back\Nwithout killing him, was quite a bother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's starting to rain.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.38,0:00:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like it'll storm.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.75,0:00:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's take cover under a tree, or we'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.56,0:00:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Leader is waiting for word that\Nwe've captured him.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.23,0:01:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Immediately thereafter, the sealing of the\N Three-Tails and Four-Tails is to occur simultaneously.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.42,0:01:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So we make him wait a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.74,0:01:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the sealing begins,\Nwe'll be working for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.18,0:01:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems near death.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.29,0:01:20.14,Default,,0,0,0,,You must handle the elderly\Nwith care.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.14,0:01:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that because\Nyou don't know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This Jinchuriki who uses the Corrosion Style\N Jutsu of the Four-Tails isn't what you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.74,0:01:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You didn't fight him yourself,\N so you wouldn't understand what I went through.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.99,0:01:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But, I was the one who asked\Nto go alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.10,0:01:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, want me to beat\Nyour assignment half-dead too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.85,0:01:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so excited, Kisame.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.92,0:01:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I'm a bit tired, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.29,0:01:59.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish we could catch all\Nthe Tailed Beasts already.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.60,0:02:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be so impatient...\NIt's going to take some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.77,0:02:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder about that.\NThere's just a few more, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.62,0:02:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's been decided that\Nthe Nine-Tails will be sealed last...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.89,0:02:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Otherwise, the balance will be disrupted,\N and the sealing statue will be pulverized...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:20.45,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Leader said...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.75,0:02:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, the Jinchuriki need\Nto be captured alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.33,0:02:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,So I say just catch them quickly\Nand leave them tied up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.29,0:02:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph... Fine with me,\Nbut remember that Deidara failed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.05,0:02:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,If he's going to be sealed last,\N it's no big deal if we capture him last.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.85,0:02:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And besides, Akatsuki is becoming\Ntoo conspicuous lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,If we capture the Nine-Tails' Jinchuriki too soon,\N the Hidden Leaf will become even more of a nuisance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh... You really think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.29,0:02:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hidden Leaf Village has\Nvery strong links with other villages.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.32,0:03:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,If they begin to collaborate,\Nit will be difficult for us to act.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:06.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be wiser to collect up to the Eight-Tails\N with as little commotion as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.12,0:03:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I guess you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.92,0:03:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There's the summons.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.55,0:03:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been caught dawdling.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.75,0:03:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.42,0:03:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We had just finished catching\Nthe Jinchuruki when you contacted us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.21,0:03:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We tied him up so he doesn't escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.11,0:03:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what took us longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.75,0:03:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.57,0:03:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I got an urgent message\NI wanted to relay to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.65,0:03:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru has been killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.00,0:03:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been ten years since\Nhe deserted us...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.51,0:03:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,So we've been spared the trouble\Nof killing him ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I would've loved to see him die as much as I\N would've loved to see the Zombie Combo die.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:04:00.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hidan and Kakuzu were our comrades.\N Don't say such things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry... Back then,\Nthey were done in by...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.89,0:04:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The Hidden Leaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.14,0:04:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The squad with Kakashi and\Nthe Nine-Tails' Jinchuriki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,They're strong, that team.\NEven Deidara got his butt kicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.56,0:04:17.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tobi!!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.67,0:04:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Say one more word and my patience\Nwill run out! It will!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.74,0:04:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It takes self-control to be patient...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,And your fuse is too short for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...! Tobi! You!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.58,0:04:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Pipe down, Deidara. Tobi's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.68,0:04:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You got chewed out!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.42,0:04:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But Tobi, you always talk too much.\NRespect your superiors.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.22,0:04:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.70,0:04:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're supposed to get\Nthe remaining Jinchuriki with these two?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.64,0:05:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But killing Orochimaru took\Nspecial skill. Who did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke Uchiha.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I was gonna be the one to\Nbring Orochimaru down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.60,0:05:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... He's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.85,0:05:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd expect nothing less from\Nyour kid brother, Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gathering members...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Really troublesome ninja at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.73,0:05:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.55,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know them well too...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.67,0:05:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,One of the Hozuki Brothers\Nof the Hidden Mist...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.17,0:05:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean, Suigetsu?\NThat brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.22,0:05:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And also, Bipolar Jugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.73,0:05:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,So be on your guard,\NItachi and Kisame...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.91,0:05:38.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I dare say they're targeting you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.22,0:05:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And the rest of you should keep\NSasuke Uchiha in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,After getting information about Itachi and Kisame,\N they may just come after the Akatsuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.24,0:05:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Kisame, what kind of guy is he...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.54,0:05:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This Suigetsu...hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.32,0:05:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.07,0:06:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He had such a cute smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.22,0:06:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,A child prodigy who's been called\N the reincarnation of the demonic Zabuza.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.03,0:06:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you a river child\Nwho got stranded on land?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.88,0:06:10.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit stopping to drink water so often!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.46,0:06:14.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmm... They seem like an interesting lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.45,0:06:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't get too interested.\NAnd just leave me out of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind that already.\N Itachi, Kisame... hurry up and get the Four-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.86,0:06:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll seal him at the same time\Nas the Three-Tails!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.19,0:06:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.37,0:06:40.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Cripes, and I thought\Nwe'd get to rest a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We have no choice. Let's hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.31,0:08:24.25,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(744.375,570)}Assemble\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.72,0:08:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We target the member of Akatsuki with whom\N we have the highest chance of meeting Sasuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.69,0:08:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can see the logic in that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.86,0:08:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Itachi Uchiha... What shall we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.29,0:08:41.48,Default,,0,0,0,,If we're able to take just one of\Nthe Akatsuki into custody,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Ibiki can get information about\NItachi out of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.69,0:08:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already issued an order to\Nall teams to capture
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.95,0:08:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a member of Akatsuki\Nif the opportunity presents itself,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.98,0:08:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,and to transport him here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,That will probably be very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.44,0:09:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kakashi Sensei...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.01,0:09:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We won't be able to make them\Ntalk so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.36,0:09:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even those we've already encountered\Nwere far too dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and we couldn't even think about\Ntaking them into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.92,0:09:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what're we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, until we come across Itachi, I don't think we\N have any choice but to be very patient and search.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.50,0:09:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go on.\NLet's take a short break...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you drag your feet like that,\Nwe'll never get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.75,0:09:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.18,0:09:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,But unlike you,\NI have a very delicate constitution.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.97,0:09:41.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Look, just evaporate,\Nyou water ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you get lost instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.49,0:09:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you had somewhere else to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.03,0:10:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.89,0:10:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've come...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.49,0:10:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, we'll begin the sealing\Nstarting with the Three-Tails.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Assemble.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.99,0:10:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:19.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.27,0:11:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What a creepy-looking place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.79,0:11:24.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.66,0:11:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A hideout in an old ruin like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.89,0:11:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's news to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.26,0:11:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru has nothing to do with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.46,0:11:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,My clan used this as a weapons store.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.42,0:11:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll prepare for the battle\Nthat will be fought here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.89,0:11:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The passageways look so similar,\Nit's easy to get lost in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:50.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But what a depressing place.\NIt stifles my breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry if it's depressing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.36,0:11:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time,\NDenka and Hina.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's young Sasuke, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.61,0:12:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your business here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.53,0:12:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your business here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.38,0:12:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Weapons and medicine...\Nand various other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.87,0:12:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,We're preparing for battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.90,0:12:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.32,0:12:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, a talking raccoon dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.70,0:12:20.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, come over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yikes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,They're ninja cats.\NDon't approach them carelessly.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.36,0:12:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll tear you apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.17,0:12:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You should warn us about stuff\Nlike that from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you bring us a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.91,0:12:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Here...a bottle of catnip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.65,0:12:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.12,0:12:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me. I'll take you to Granny Cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe you, Granny Cat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been so long since we've met,\Nbut you're in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.79,0:12:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I have something important to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.59,0:13:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not a ninja cat, right?\NThere, there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.16,0:13:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stop. Even this one is too small.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.93,0:13:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.72,0:13:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're going to see Itachi,\Nafter all?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.43,0:13:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I've known you both since\Nyou were little,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.33,0:13:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,but little did I imagine\Nit would come to this...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.03,0:13:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You two are all that's left\Nof the Uchiha Clan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.09,0:13:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, you'll have to\Nfight to the death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going. Thanks for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny, don't we have something bigger\Nfor him to wear?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In that box over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.84,0:13:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.16,0:13:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Then just wrap that curtain\Naround him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.83,0:13:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't run a clothing store!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.68,0:13:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny! What a rude thing to say,\Nconsidering he paid us!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.23,0:13:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.57,0:14:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Pursue Itachi in order to meet up\Nwith Sasuke, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.23,0:14:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then...\NSay we find Itachi. What next?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.37,0:14:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,About that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.83,0:14:15.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I have an idea.\NCan you spare some time?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.51,0:14:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't look too pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.05,0:14:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Pervy Sage?\NWhat're you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.03,0:14:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I hadn't seen my apprentice in a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.15,0:14:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,so I thought maybe\Nwe could share a meal.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:40.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you treating?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.33,0:14:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Cripes, what's with Kakashi Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.03,0:14:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, we're ready to move out\Nany time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.16,0:14:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.\NThere are lots of things to prepare for.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.17,0:14:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare for what?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.28,0:14:57.12,Default,,0,0,0,,One small squad isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.29,0:15:00.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.46,0:15:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen. If Itachi is defeated,\N Sasuke will lose his purpose in coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:08.21,Default,,0,0,0,,So we have no choice\Nbut to find a way to detain Itachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.55,0:15:13.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And that will require a coordinated effort\Nwith more ninja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.46,0:15:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, Kakashi has his hands full\Ntrying to get this organized.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.16,0:15:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.23,0:15:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But we're dealing with Itachi here.\NOrdinary methods won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.83,0:15:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably not...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And we can't just avoid him, can we?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.12,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And just bring Sasuke back?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you understand,\N but Sasuke has grown powerful enough to kill Orochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.06,0:15:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I made a promise\Nto Sakura long ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That I'd "bring Sasuke back without fail."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:51.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And I can't go back on my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.39,0:16:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What is most important to a ninja\N is not the number of jutsu he possesses...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.11,0:16:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What's important is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.27,0:16:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,- To never give up!\N- To never give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.98,0:16:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Determination!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.39,0:16:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That's my Ninja Way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.86,0:16:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as foolish as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.69,0:16:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.05,0:16:19.47,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm the apprentice\Nof the Pervy Sage.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.59,0:16:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, what a rude apprentice\NI'm stuck with.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.00,0:16:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"Rude"?! What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.68,0:16:31.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly that, you rude apprentice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.34,0:16:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You're one to talk, Pervy Sage!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.35,0:16:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a no-good, perverted old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.19,0:16:37.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, eat this too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.56,0:16:40.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.82,0:16:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ichiraku's roast pork is still the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.38,0:17:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Cripes, sealing the Tailed Beast\Nis such a pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.88,0:17:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,And there's more to go after this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Just thinking about it annoys me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:14.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then... which way? Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm... Excuse me, Senpai,\N"which way" what?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.31,0:17:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.97,0:17:21.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.81,0:17:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Do we go for the Nine-Tails' Jinchuriki and Kakashi...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.65,0:17:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,or Sasuke Uchiha...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.66,0:17:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, we shouldn't mess with either one!\N Our assignment is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.18,0:17:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,And furthermore,\NSasuke's not even a Tailed Beast!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.70,0:17:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.83,0:17:43.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The Nine-Tails' Jinchuriki owes me one\Nfor punching me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.16,0:17:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,And Kakashi got my right arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.09,0:17:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's Sasuke Uchiha...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.18,0:17:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive him 'cuz he killed\NOrochimaru, whom I planned to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.80,0:17:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.38,0:17:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Once he sets his mind to something,\Nhe just won't listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.05,0:18:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.69,0:18:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.31,0:18:04.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph. We're going, Tobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear... That Deidara has gotten all worked\N up about going after your little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that okay with you, Itachi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.43,0:18:43.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.89,0:18:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. You've given it\Nquite a bit of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.93,0:19:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, shouldn't we have even more guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.88,0:19:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not simply a matter of manpower.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.61,0:19:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,For this job, I think two squads\Nworking together are ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,If our targets are few in number,\Nnamely one or two,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.28,0:19:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,having more than three squads will make us too\N easy to detect and disrupts the chain of command.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.41,0:19:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,And it will end up hindering our mobility.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.69,0:19:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Restraining the enemy requires\Nmuch more technique than mere killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.02,0:19:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,In coordinating the squads, it's wise to choose\N members who are accustomed to working together.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.41,0:19:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, right now,\Nthis is the best plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.13,0:19:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're about ready to set out,\Nbut I don't like this weather.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.46,0:19:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The rain is perfect for cooling off someone\Nso fired up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.63,0:19:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm issuing the order\Nfor a mission
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.59,0:20:00.83,Default,,0,0,0,,to locate and detain Itachi Uchiha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.23,0:20:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,All of you, be extremely careful\Nand carry out your duties!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.47,0:20:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,- Right!\N- Right!
